03:31.018 --> 03:32.018
Hey!

03:32.020 --> 03:33.469
Leave alone! No money
in the register!

03:33.471 --> 03:35.021
No, no, I got to
make an order!

03:35.023 --> 03:37.306
Closed. Come back tomorrow.

03:37.308 --> 03:39.775
But, hey... it's Danny Reagan.

03:39.777 --> 03:41.944
You remember my dad, the cop?

03:44.898 --> 03:47.200
Hi.
Danny Reagan.

03:47.202 --> 03:49.202
Yeah.
You used to be this tall.

03:49.204 --> 03:50.203
I know.

03:50.205 --> 03:51.854
Well, we are still closed.

03:51.856 --> 03:53.322
No, come... look, my
wife's gonna kill me

03:53.324 --> 03:54.857
if I don't get
this order in.

03:54.859 --> 03:56.209
You got to
help me out.

03:56.211 --> 03:59.962
Uh, I have wife like that.

03:59.964 --> 04:02.081
Tell you what,
you tell me what you want,

04:02.083 --> 04:03.666
I make it myself.

04:03.668 --> 04:05.084
Okay, good.
Come in.

04:05.086 --> 04:06.535
That'll make my
family very happy.

04:06.537 --> 04:08.087
You get warm.
Yeah.

04:26.524 --> 04:29.692
Are you kidding me?

04:46.209 --> 04:48.177
Sir?
Hey.

04:48.179 --> 04:50.296
Can I see your license
and registration?

04:50.298 --> 04:52.081
Will that work?

04:54.184 --> 04:55.417
I'm on the job.

04:55.419 --> 04:57.136
Oh.

04:57.138 --> 04:59.188
Evening, Detective.

04:59.190 --> 05:00.773
Good evening to you, too.

05:00.775 --> 05:02.925
You mind if I take a look
around in the back?

05:02.927 --> 05:04.310
You're joking, right?

05:04.312 --> 05:05.928
I wish I was.

05:05.930 --> 05:08.564
But 911 got an anonymous
tip about a drug sale.

05:08.566 --> 05:10.599
Says a car
matching this one

05:10.601 --> 05:12.618
is in the area
to make the drop.

05:12.620 --> 05:15.321
Look, you know I can make you
get a warrant for this.

05:15.323 --> 05:17.957
That's why I'm hoping
for your cooperation, Detective.

05:17.959 --> 05:20.660
Right, why waste
anyone else's time tonight

05:20.662 --> 05:22.828
besides mine?

05:22.830 --> 05:24.279
Excuse me.

05:27.301 --> 05:28.551
I'm telling you

05:28.553 --> 05:30.386
there's nothing in there
but a bunch of old junk

05:30.388 --> 05:31.804
I'm bringing home
from the squad.

05:33.674 --> 05:36.342
The door sticks.

05:37.978 --> 05:39.562
See?

05:39.564 --> 05:41.063
Box of junk.

05:44.067 --> 05:45.368
Move the box.

05:45.370 --> 05:46.969
Why do I got to move the box?

05:46.971 --> 05:48.470
It's just an old box of junk!

05:51.358 --> 05:52.408
What is that?

05:53.276 --> 05:54.860
Looks like cocaine to me.

05:54.862 --> 05:56.579
That's not mine.
Step away from the vehicle.

05:56.581 --> 05:57.863
Look, I'm telling you,

05:57.865 --> 05:59.365
I don't know how
that got in my car!

05:59.367 --> 06:00.700
Put your hands
on the glass.

06:00.702 --> 06:03.419
Come on, it's...
Put your hands on the glass!

06:05.488 --> 06:07.673
I don't know how
that got in the car.

